Package command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Command
    A general Command interface having the functions undo and redo.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddToBodyCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block got connected as a Body to a surroundingBlock.
    AddToBodyFunctionDefinitionCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block got connected as a Body to a surroundingBlock.
    ConnectCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block got connected to another block.
    DeleteBlockCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block is deleted.
    DeleteCallerCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block is deleted.
    DeleteFunctionDefinitionCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block is deleted.
    DisconnectCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block got disconnected to another block.
    DraggingCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block gets dragged from one place to another.
    ExecutionCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the execution by a block (currently executed) that is not an actionBlock.
    MakeBlockCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block is made.
    MakeFunctionCommand  
    SetConditionCommand
    A class that holds all the information about the action where a block got connected as a condition to a surroundingBlock.
